  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You carve smoldering seals into your flesh, which remain dormant until activated as an attack action.<br><br>When activated, you can make a ray attack against a target within 20 ft, dealing 2d6 force damage and, if the target is no larger than Medium size, knocking it back 1d4 x 5 ft. The subject also falls @Condition[prone]{prone} (Fortitude negates). Alternatively, you can make an unarmed attack against an adjacent foe, adding the damage and effects of the ray to the attack if it hits. CR applies to the activation effect of the seal.<br><br>This technique takes up one seal slot, and you deal yourself 2 damage when performing it.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 3 Chakra and deal yourself 2 additional damage to increase both the damage and the knockback by 1 die.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
